Key Match Events: David Wiese scored 13 runs and dismissed Oman's Naseem Khushi in the super over
Ruben Trumpelmann took four wickets for Oman in the regular 20 overs
Mehran Khan took three wickets for Oman in the final over
Namibia needed just five runs to win in the super over
Post-Match Reflections: David Wiese said he aged a couple of years and the evening was emotionally draining
Oman captain Aqib Ilyas defended the decision to use Bilal Khan in the super over
Miscellaneous Highlights: Namibia needed 22 runs to win in the super over
